N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 756.6 - Quality assurance

State Regulations

In addition to the requirements set forth in section
751.8
of this Title, the operator
shall ensure that there is a review of any abortion procedure complication with
the use of these findings in the development and revision of policies and in
consideration of renewing or granting staff privileges. Notes
